{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-classic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/responsive-web-design/applied-visual-design/make-motion-more-natural-using-a-bezier-curve","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"block":"applied-visual-design","demoType":null,"title":"Ucini kretanje prirodnijim pomocu Bezier krive","description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Ovaj izazov animira element tako da imitira kretanje bacene lopte. Prethodni izazovi su ukljucivali <code>linear</code> i <code>ease-out</code> kubne Bezier krive, ali nijedna ne prikazuje realistican let lopte. Zato je potrebno prilagoditi Bezier krivu.</p>\n<p><code>animation-timing-function</code> se automatski ponavlja za svaki keyframe kada je <code>animation-iteration-count</code> postavljen na beskonacno. Posto postoji keyframe pravilo na sredini trajanja animacije (na <code>50%</code>), nastaje sekvenca koja se ponavlja dva puta u kretanju lopte nagore i nadole.</p>\n<p>Sledeca kubna Bezier kriva imitira kretanje bacene lopte:</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-css\">cubic-bezier(0.3, 0.4, 0.5, 1.6);\n</code></pre>\n<p>Primetite da je vrednost y2 veca od 1. Iako je kubna Bezier kriva postavljena u koordinatni sistem 1x1 i x vrednosti mogu biti samo od 0 do 1, y vrednost moze biti i veca od 1. To proizvodi efekat odskoka, sto je odlicno za simulaciju lopte koja se baca.</p>\n</section>","id":"587d78a9367417b2b2512aea","hasEditableBoundaries":false,"instructions":"<section id=\"instructions\">\n<p>Promenite <code>animation-timing-function</code> vrednost elementa sa id <code>green</code> u <code>cubic-bezier</code> funkciju sa x1, y1, x2, y2 vrednostima 0.311, 0.441, 0.444, 1.649.</p>\n</section>","notes":null,"challengeType":0,"helpCategory":"HTML-CSS","videoUrl":"https://scrimba.com/c/c7akWUv","superBlock":"responsive-web-design","translationPending":false,"forumTopicId":301063,"hooks":null,"fields":{"slug":"/learn/responsive-web-design/applied-visual-design/make-motion-more-natural-using-a-bezier-curve"},"required":[],"usesMultifileEditor":false,"challengeFiles":[{"fileKey":"indexhtml","ext":"html","name":"index","contents":"<style>\n  .balls {\n    border-radius: 50%;\n    position: fixed;\n    width: 50px;\n    height: 50px;\n    top: 60%;\n    animation-name: jump;\n    animation-duration: 2s;\n    animation-iteration-count: infinite;\n  }\n  #red {\n    background: red;\n    left: 25%;\n    animation-timing-function: linear;\n  }\n  #blue {\n    background: blue;\n    left: 50%;\n    animation-timing-function: ease-out;\n  }\n  #green {\n    background: green;\n    left: 75%;\n    animation-timing-function: cubic-bezier(0.69, 0.1, 1, 0.1);\n  }\n\n  @keyframes jump {\n    50% {\n      top: 10%;\n    }\n  }\n</style>\n<div class=\"balls\" id=\"red\"></div>\n<div class=\"balls\" id=\"blue\"></div>\n<div class=\"balls\" id=\"green\"></div>","head":null,"tail":null,"editableRegionBoundaries":[],"history":["index.html"]}],"saveSubmissionToDB":null,"tests":[{"text":"<p><code>animation-timing-function</code> vrednost za element sa id <code>green</code> treba da bude <code>cubic-bezier</code> funkcija sa navedenim x1, y1, x2, y2 vrednostima.</p>","testString":"const greenElement = document.querySelector('#green');\n const greenStyle = window.getComputedStyle(greenElement);\nassert.equal(greenStyle?.animationTimingFunction, 'cubic-bezier(0.311, 0.441, 0.444, 1.649)');"}]}}},"pageContext":{"challengeMeta":{"blockHashSlug":"/learn/responsive-web-design/#applied-visual-design","dashedName":"make-motion-more-natural-using-a-bezier-curve","certification":"responsive-web-design","disableLoopProtectTests":false,"disableLoopProtectPreview":false,"superBlock":"responsive-web-design","chapter":null,"module":null,"block":"applied-visual-design","isFirstStep":false,"template":null,"required":[],"isLastChallengeInBlock":true,"nextChallengePath":"/learn/responsive-web-design/applied-accessibility/add-a-text-alternative-to-images-for-visually-impaired-accessibility","prevChallengePath":"/learn/responsive-web-design/applied-visual-design/use-a-bezier-curve-to-move-a-graphic","id":"587d78a9367417b2b2512aea","saveSubmissionToDB":null},"projectPreview":{"challengeData":{"challengeType":0,"challengeFiles":[{"name":"index","ext":"html","contents":"<style>\n  .balls {\n    border-radius: 50%;\n    position: fixed;\n    width: 50px;\n    height: 50px;\n    top: 60%;\n    animation-name: jump;\n    animation-duration: 2s;\n    animation-iteration-count: infinite;\n  }\n  #red {\n    background: red;\n    left: 25%;\n    animation-timing-function: linear;\n  }\n  #blue {\n    background: blue;\n    left: 50%;\n    animation-timing-function: ease-out;\n  }\n  #green {\n    background: green;\n    left: 75%;\n    animation-timing-function: cubic-bezier(0.311, 0.441, 0.444, 1.649);\n  }\n\n  @keyframes jump {\n    50% {\n      top: 10%;\n    }\n  }\n</style>\n<div class=\"balls\" id=\"red\"></div>\n<div class=\"balls\" id=\"blue\"></div>\n<div class=\"balls\" id=\"green\"></div>","history":["index.html"],"fileKey":"indexhtml"}]}},"id":"/learn/responsive-web-design/applied-visual-design/make-motion-more-natural-using-a-bezier-curve"}},"staticQueryHashes":["3858520367"],"slicesMap":{}}